\begin_inset Formula $q$
\end_inset 

.
 This is false because, in fact, 
\begin_inset Formula $\mbox{Li}_{s}\left(z\right)$
\end_inset 

 has a branch point at 
\begin_inset Formula $z=1$
\end_inset 

.
 The 
